snippet.title: 2016 FULL WORLD SET McDONALD'S SING MOVIE HAPPY MEAL TOYS 12 KIDS COLLECTION REVIEW EUROPE ASIA USA
snippet.description:
Here at Fast Food Toys we review the next new 2016 McDonald's  Illumination Sing movie Happy Meal toys world set collection of 12 kids meal toys. The SING movie will be out in theaters on December 21, 2016 and we can't wait to see it! It's by the same creators as the Despicable Me, Minions & the Secret Life Of Pets movies. The 2016 - 2017 toys feature animals porcupine Ash, koala Buster Moon, iguana Ms. Crawly, white mouse Mike, gorilla Johnny, 2 pigs Rosita & Gunter & elephant Meena and the Q-Teez red pandas cuties, they look like cute foxes! These Happy Meal toys will be available in many countries around the world including the USA, Canada, Europe (e.g. Austria, Germany, Switzerland, Spain, Italy, Turkey, UK), Asia (e.g. Thailand, China, Malaysia, Singapore, Philippines), Australia and Latin America! In Mexico, they are known as canta pelicula cajita feliz juguetes while in Brazil it's known as cantar filme mclanche feliz brinquedos. The Sing McDonald's Happy Meal toys will be available at McDonalds restaurants in December 2016 and January 2017. There are talking toys, singing toys and moving toys. There are 2 different Rositas. she sings and dances and 2 different Meenas. There are lots of songs and dances in the Sing movie. There are some more variations to the Sing talking toys such as in German.

The Sing movie is based on a singing contest similar to American Idol and The Voice competition shows. We love the Sing movie trailers and can't wait to see the Sing Happy Meal toys commercials!

The previous McDonald's toys were the TMNT and Hello Sanrio toys from November to December 2016.

Everyone knows the best part of blockbuster movies are the fun toys that come with it! Here at FastFoodToyReviews we have collected every toy from Hollywood’s best feature films from almost every decade. From American classics like Back to the Future, and the Lion King to modern day favorites like Minions, Jurassic World and Big Hero 6, we have gathered every fast food toy collection just for you. Remember the Simpson’s collection at Burger King from their feature film? How about the Pixar Movie collection from McDonald’s? Or what about the interlocking toys from the first Ice Age or Rugrats Movie? How about the multiple collections of Scooby-Doo and Shrek toys? Well those are just a few of the favorites we don’t want you to miss!

About FastFoodToyReviews
Think toys are limited to Toys R Us and other big Toy Stores? Well, not here at FastFoodToyReviews! We know some of the best toys come from the Fast Food Toy Chest. Join us as we scour every McDonald’s Menu for the newest Happy Meal toys, travel to every Burger King for the newest movie collectable, and check out every Wendy’s --- but that’s more for the delicious Frosties. For years fast food restaurants have always made toys with our favorite characters, like Scooby-Doo, Disney classics like Toy Story and the Nickelodeon gang, but it took a true collector, like FastFoodToyReviews to find and collect them all. So subscribe today and join us we go through every drive through to find and share our favorite toys with you!​​​
